Class TargetedCombinerParameterMap<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacmlatt.pdp.policy.TargetedCombinerParameterMap<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the identifier for the TargetedCombinerParameters in the map
    U - the type of the object referenced by the identifier

    public class TargetedCombinerParameterMap<T,U>
extends java.lang.Object
    TargetedCombinerParameterMap is a utility for maintaining a collection of com.att.research.xacmlatt.policy.TargetedCombinerParameter objects with the mappings to their targets.
